<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>Black & Gold Elegance</title>
  <style>
    body {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: 'Quicksand', sans-serif;
      background: linear-gradient(to right top, #000000, #434343);
      color: #f5f5f5;
    }

    header {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 50px 20px 20px;
      background: #1a1a1a;
    }

    h1 {
      font-family: 'MonterchiTextBook';
      font-size: 3.5rem;
      color: #ffd700;
      text-shadow: 2px 2px #000;
    }

    p {
      max-width: 900px;
      margin: 20px auto;
      padding: 0 20px;
      font-family: 'MonterchiTextBook';
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      line-height: 1.7;
      color: #f0e6cc;
    }

    .container {
      max-width: 1100px;
      margin: 40px auto;
      padding: 0 20px;
    }

    .theme-section {
      background: #2b2b2b;
      border-radius: 15px;
      padding: 20px;
      margin-bottom: 40px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(255, 215, 0, 0.2);
    }

    .theme-section h2 {
      color: #ffd700;
      text-align: center;
      font-family: 'MonterchiTextBook';
    }

    .theme-section img {
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 300px;
      height: 300px;
      border-radius: 10px;
      object-fit: cover;
      margin: 1rem;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(255, 215, 0, 0.3);
    }

    .theme-section ul {
      list-style-type: none;
      padding-left: 0;
    }

    .theme-section li {
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      background: #3a3a3a;
      padding: 15px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 10px rgba(255, 215, 0, 0.1);
      font-family: 'MonterchiTextBook';
    }

    @media screen and (max-width: 600px) {
      .theme-section .card-img {
        width: 90%;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <header>
    <h1>Black & Gold Elegance</h1>
  </header>

  <p>Indulge in sophistication with our “Black & Gold Elegance” theme—perfect for upscale birthdays, milestone celebrations, and classy evening affairs. A luxurious combination of dark tones and shimmering gold details makes this party truly unforgettable and glamorous!</p>

  <div class="container">

    <section class="theme-section">
      <h2>Theme Details & Decoration Setup</h2>
      <img src="img/elegance1.jpg" alt="Gold Table Setting" class="card-img">
      <img src="img/elegance2.jpg" alt="Black and Gold Backdrop" class="card-img">
      <img src="img/elegance3.jpg" alt="Elegant Dessert Display" class="card-img">
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Theme Ideas:</strong><br>Host a “Golden Gala,” “Luxury Noir Night,” or “Midnight Sparkle Soirée” with glitzy black and gold décor.</li>
        <li><strong>Decor Detail:</strong><br>Think velvet tablecloths, metallic balloons, candlelight, sequined drapes, golden chargers, and crystal accents.</li>
        <li><strong>Color Palette Inspiration:</strong><br>Jet black, metallic gold, champagne, and soft ivory tones.</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="theme-section">
      <h2>Decoration & Setup Guide</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>✨ Welcome guests with a golden carpet entrance and glittering archway.</li>
        <li>✨ Use black and gold place settings with elegant name cards and cutlery.</li>
        <li>✨ Add floral arrangements with white roses, orchids, and golden leaves.</li>
        <li>✨ Set up a champagne tower or gold-rimmed glasses for toasts.</li>
        <li>✨ Serve luxe treats like gold-dusted macarons, dark chocolate truffles, and sparkling cupcakes.</li>
        <li>✨ Provide elegant dress code hints—black tie or cocktail glam.</li>
        <li>✨ Create a chic photo booth with a sequined backdrop and golden props.</li>
        <li>✨ Include a golden guestbook or memory jar for well wishes.</li>
        <li>✨ Hand out classy favors like mini candles, custom gold keychains, or engraved pens.</li>
        <li>✨ Wrap the night with a graceful dance or a toast under hanging fairy lights!</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

  </div>

</body>
</html>
